Saya akan uruskan untuk awak.

282
00:20:43,823 --> 00:20:44,823
sorakan.

283
00:20:45,623 --> 00:20:47,090
terima kasih.

284
00:20:49,923 --> 00:20:52,523
Bagaimana perasaan anda? Sudah hilangkah rindu itu?

285
00:20:52,723 --> 00:20:55,057
Memang, tetapi saya mahu berjumpa dengannya lagi.

286
00:20:55,523 --> 00:20:57,423
Dia nampaknya sukakan awak.

287
00:20:57,990 --> 00:20:59,290
Saya akan bawa awak melawat dia lagi.

288
00:20:59,890 --> 00:21:00,957
Di mana anda telah pergi?

289
00:21:02,623 --> 00:21:03,923
Awak balik lambat.

290
00:21:05,357 --> 00:21:07,957
Aku bawa Arisa jumpa Auntie Ruwajee.

291
00:21:10,023 --> 00:21:11,157
Ruwajee?

292
00:21:12,223 --> 00:21:12,990
