tetapi saya harap itu sahaja yang ada.

304
00:21:58,357 --> 00:22:00,023
- Sayang. - Hm?

305
00:22:00,823 --> 00:22:02,257
Tentang Auntie Ruwajee,

306
00:22:03,723 --> 00:22:06,223
